  gnome-mount-0.4-r5.ebuild:
  Add ~alpha keyword.

*gnome-mount-0.4-r5 (25 Aug 2006)

  25 Aug 2006; Patrick McLean <chutzpah@gentoo.org>
  +files/gnome-mount-0.4-ntfs3g.patch, +gnome-mount-0.4-r5.ebuild:
  New revision, add patch to support mounting NTFS drives with ntfs-3g.

